OL,3,CHeroes describe dramatic sinking car
OL,4,Crescue
OL,6,FThe three rescuers told ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian they jumped into the sea to
OL,8,Fhelp a sinking driver without thinking.
OL,10,FThree people who saved a man from his
OL,11,Fsinking car after it rolled into the
OL,12,Fsea at Sandbanks, have spoken of the
OL,13,Fdramatic rescue.
OL,15,FShaw Vallance was among the men who
OL,16,Fjumped into the water to save the 72-
OL,17,Fyear-old driver on Tuesday. He says it
OL,18,Fcould have been a much bigger tragedy.
OL,20,FRobert Hill is doing well considering
OL,21,Fhis ordeal.
