OL,6,FBut along with the shock of plunging
OL,7,Finto the water and then being trapped,
OL,8,Fwhat he remembers most is the help
OL,9,Ffrom strangers.
OL,11,FSitting on one of these benches,
OL,12,Fnarrowly missed by the accelerating
OL,13,Fcar, was Shaw Vallance, along with his
OL,14,Fpartner and seven-month-old son.
OL,16,FWhen he realised someone was in the
OL,17,Fcar he jumped into the water.
