OL,6,FShaw said, "I made it to the car and
OL,7,Fat the point I was on the bonnet I
OL,8,Fthink I was met by some other people
OL,9,Fwho helped pull him out.
OL,11,F"I tried the door first of all and I
OL,12,Fknew it wasn't going to open because
OL,13,Fof the water obviously but you do what
OL,14,Fyou can.
