OL,3,CHeroes describe dramatic sinking car
OL,4,Crescue
OL,6,F"It was at that point I really
OL,7,Fappreciated the help to be honest. I
OL,8,Fcan swim but I don't know if I'd have
OL,9,Fbeen able to get him to the shoreline
OL,10,Fon my own so to have the help pulling
OL,11,Fhim out and get to the shoreline was
OL,12,Freally appreciated."
OL,14,FThat help came from a group of men on
OL,15,Fa fishing trip. Among them, Abdeliah
OL,16,FSlah and Abdel Hamid Bakkali.
OL,18,FAbdeliah said, "I saw the man jump in
OL,19,Fand I said to myself, one person is
OL,20,Fnot enough, so I threw myself on the
OL,21,Fwater.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
