OL,6,F"I said, my friend, don't worry, we
OL,7,Fare here to help you, you are in safe
OL,8,Fhands.
OL,10,FAbdel said, "Robert told me, when we
OL,11,Fput him in the back, he told me he'd
OL,12,Fjust washed that car today."
OL,14,FThe men say they didn't catch a fish
OL,15,Fthat day, but instead they caught a
OL,16,Fhuman.
OL,18,FRobert earlier described how he was
OL,19,Fpulled out of the car and taken to
OL,20,Fsafety.
