OL,6,FAnd that would also have been
OL,7,Fdevastating for those trying to rescue
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,F"At that moment you don't really think
OL,11,Fabout what you're doing, you act on
OL,12,Finstinct, but you kind of struggle a
OL,13,Fbit afterwards to think what could
OL,14,Fhave gone wrong, for him, for me.
