OL,3,CHeroes describe dramatic sinking car
OL,4,Crescue
OL,6,F"I wouldn't say it was the most
OL,7,Fresponsible thing, having a seven-
OL,8,Fmonth-old child, jumping in the water
OL,9,Fbut, like I said, you act on instinct
OL,10,Fand he needed help, so myself and the
OL,11,Fother gentlemen did and luckily
OL,12,Feveryone got out safely,"
OL,14,FRobert says he owes his life to the
OL,15,Frescuers and he can't thank them
OL,16,Fenough.
